{"lemma":"مَشْرَباتٌ","slug":"مَشْرَباتٌ","root":"ش.ر.ب","root_slug":"ش-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَشْرَب","root":"شرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22051","n22054"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place for drinking","tags":["literally"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place for drinking; pub, bar","tags":["literally"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"drink, beverage","examples":[{"text":"وَلَهُمْ فِيهَا مَنَافِعُ وَمَشَارِبُ أَفَلَا يَشْكُرُونَ","english":"And they derive from them other benefits and drinks. Will they not then give thanks?"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the verb شَرِبَ (šariba, “to drink”)."},"ipa":["/maʃ.rab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22051","headword_ar":"مَشْرَبٌ","root":"$rb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is a noun of place, [and of time,] as well as an inf. n.: [i. e.] it signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a time, of drinking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quarter"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajoh","text_ar":"وَجْه"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whence one drinks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place to which one comes to drink at a river"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rivulet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$orabapN","text_ar":"مَشْرَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, TA,) not, as is implied in the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$orubapN","text_ar":"مَشْرُبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (TA,) signifies [the same, as"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1529},{"kind":"text","text":"is indicated in the A; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place whence people drink;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oraEapN","text_ar":"مَشْرَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oraEap","text_ar":"مَشْرَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA ma$orabu Alqawomi","text_ar":"هٰذَا مَشْرَبُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$orabatuhumo","text_ar":"مَشْرَبَتُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is the people's,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party's, drinkingplace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place whence they drink"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And it is said in a trad., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maloEuwnN mano A^aHaATa EalaY ma$orabapK","text_ar":"مَلْعُونٌ مَنْ اَحَاطَ عَلَى مَشْرَبَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cursed is he"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who takes entirely to himself, debarring others from it, a place whence people drink."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irobN","text_ar":"شِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","TA","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n22054","headword_ar":"مِشْرَبٌ","root":"$rb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irobN","text_ar":"شِرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aruwbN","text_ar":"شَرُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}